      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARLIGHT TORY (2) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 10 length sixth (30.80) at this track in a Grade 5. Tough to beat on best. TWIN FIN (1) fast out of the inside draw with a slick early sectional and clocking 30.01 in a 5.5 lengths win at this track over 520m last time. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. One of main contenders. IMPRESS MOANA (5) was in the minors two back (29.96) at this track but ran below best last time at Mandurah, finishing 7th. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from five starts. Cannot be underestimated. RAPIDO ACE (4) is in winning form and worth including in the main hopes.",
